WEBVTT

00:03.563 --> 00:04.909
If you're looking to save money,...

00:04.975 --> 00:07.130
...you could bicycle to work instead of driving.

00:07.636 --> 00:09.450
And if you really want to save money,...

00:09.872 --> 00:11.916
...you could make your bike your home.

00:12.470 --> 00:17.224
Designer Kacey Wong made this thing in response to sky-high Hong Kong rents.

00:17.629 --> 00:18.520
Ready for the tour?

00:19.423 --> 00:25.364
Door, window, desk, bed and that's it.

00:26.045 --> 00:27.903
Good luck bringing a girl back there, Kacey.

